fwprop.note:
Start Action for Command (12,23) to add one or more functional monitor (FMON) definitions. 
The command carries a list of functional monitor definitions to be added to the FMDL
(Functional Monitoring Definition List). The index i iterates over all the FMONs in the command.

fwprop.note:
This procedure generates a (1,4) report for each rejected functional monitor
definition in the command. The (1,4) reports are generated by the Command
Verification Failure Procedure. The start action is declared successful as long 
as at least one valid functional monitor definition is accepted for execution.
